<Layout titleZh="AI 前沿周报 | 谢灵江" titleEn="AI Frontier Weekly | James Xie" descriptionZh="AI 前沿周报，汇总大厂动态、学术进展与社区工程趋势。" descriptionEn="An AI frontier weekly covering big tech moves, academic progress, and community engineering trends." ogImage="/og-briefings.svg">
  <section class="bg-dark px-4 py-20 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4 text-white">
        <span class="lang-zh">AI 前沿<span class="text-gold">周报</span></span>
        <span class="lang-en hidden">AI Frontier <span class="text-gold">Weekly</span></span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-400 mb-12">
        <span class="lang-zh">来自 Scout Agent 的最新外部情报精选</span>
        <span class="lang-en hidden">A curated digest of the latest external signals gathered by Scout Agent</span>
      </p>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
        <span class="lang-zh">最后更新：2026年05月14日</span>
        <span class="lang-en hidden">Last updated: May 14, 2026
      </p>
      <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-gold mx-auto mb-16"></div>

      <div class="mb-16 p-8 bg-gold/5 border border-gold/30 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold mb-4 flex items-center">
          <span class="mr-3">🧠</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">首要信号</span>
          <span class="lang-en hidden">Executive Summary</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="text-gray-300 space-y-4 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            <span class="lang-zh">今日实时抓取的 Scout 简报显示，<strong class="text-white">"格局重置"</strong>成为本周核心主题。马斯克解散 xAI 并转型算力供应商，月之暗面完成中国大模型史上最大融资，Anthropic 推出 Claude "做梦"记忆功能。AI 行业正从模型能力的单维比拼，切换为算力基建、资本捆绑和生态卡位的立体战争。</span>
            <span class="lang-en hidden">Real-time signals from today's Scout briefing highlight <strong class="text-white">"Paradigm Reset"</strong> as this week's core theme. Musk dissolves xAI and transitions to compute supplier, Moonshot AI completes China's largest LLM funding round, and Anthropic launches Claude's "Dreaming" memory feature. The AI industry is shifting from single-dimensional model capability competition to a multi-dimensional war of compute infrastructure, capital bundling, and ecosystem positioning.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      {sections.map((section) => (
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold mb-8 flex items-center">
            <span class="mr-3">{section.icon}</span>
            <span class="lang-zh">{section.title.zh}</span>
            <span class="lang-en hidden">{section.title.en}</span>
          </h2>
          {section.items.length > 0 ? (
            <div class="space-y-6">
              {section.items.map((item) => (
                <article class="group p-6 border-l-2 border-gold/30 hover:border-gold transition-colors hover:bg-dark/50">
                  <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white group-hover:text-gold transition-colors">
                      <span class="lang-zh">{item.title.zh}</span>
                      <span class="lang-en hidden">{item.title.en}</span>
                    </h3>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 whitespace-nowrap ml-4">{item.date}</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">
                    <span class="lang-zh">{item.summary.zh}</span>
                    <span class="lang-en hidden">{item.summary.en}</span>
                  </p>
                  {item.links && item.links.length > 0 && (
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                      {item.links.map((link) => (
                        <a href={link.href} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-gold text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">{link.label}</a>
                      ))}
                    </div>
                  )}
                </article>
              ))}
            </div>
          ) : (
            <div class="p-6 border border-gold/20 rounded-lg bg-dark/40 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              <span class="lang-zh">本期未出现高置信度、值得单独入选的社区与工程信号，因此暂不额外列出。</span>
              <span class="lang-en hidden">No high-confidence community or engineering signal stood out strongly enough this cycle to warrant a dedicated entry.</span>
            </div>
          )}
        </div>
      ))}

      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <a href="/" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 border-2 border-gold text-gold hover:bg-gold hover:text-dark transition-all font-semibold">
          <span class="lang-zh">返回首页</span>
          <span class="lang-en hidden">Back to Home</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
